data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Lucien Fields neighborhood. This immaculate residence exudes modern elegance and boasts a range of luxurious upgrades that set it apart from the rest. Step into a home that still exudes the freshness of newness, adorned with stunning ceramic wood flooring. Spacious Open Floorplan: Perfectly designed for those who love to entertain, the open floorplan seamlessly connects living, dining, and kitchen areas, providing an inviting atmosphere for gatherings, parties, or simply relaxing. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the gourmet kitchen. Featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a generously sized island with loads of counter space to entertain. With four spacious bedrooms and three well-appointed bathrooms, there is room for everyone. Enjoy your peaceful back porch with no back neighbors and fully fenced-in! Close to shopping and restaurants.
